[h3 
	" Basic timesavers
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"NOTE: Many of these timesavers were not used in the beginning (the most suitable part for these timesavers of the game) 
	$LF
	"since I discovered them later in the run and forgot to use them in my final version where I started from a later room.
	$LF
]p
[ol 
	[li 
		" While having the biggest horizontal momentum and being in mid-air, just repress "A" without "->" or "<-" and you almost won't lose momentum.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Two slides or more are faster than running.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" It is possible to get into a ceiling with the upper part of Kirby's body by flying towards it from left or right. It was mostly used while being rocket. For example, in the water area, in the last room before the shark, it was possible to skip some blocks this way.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" If horizontal momentum is needed after entering a room or quitting a slide animation it's the best to start the running animation and then jumping immediately. I forgot to use it in the earlier parts as well.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Jumping towards a door and entering it is 1 frame faster than doing so without jumping.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" It is possible to press Down or Up in water and swim into a direction for 10 frames or so without canceling the swimming-animation.
		$LF
	]li
]ol
[p 
	"There are more, but they are more specific and minor.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Possible improvements I know about
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"All the things I mentioned above should be used everywhere when possible.
	$LF
	"And the boss fights could be improved. I often redid a boss fight two times and then continued with the fastest result.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Improving a run of such a game may be hard or easy, as the game is sometimes quite random. Your Kirby buddies are fooling around while you're going your path. In one of my earlier attempts I went through the great mirror to the endbosses with Red Kirby so that Dark Mind 4 was even harder to luckmanipulate.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"I know some more timesavers than listed here. 
	$LF
	"So if someone wants to improve the run, PM me on the forums.
	$LF
]p
